{"id": 1791, "genre": 1000, "title": "你是哪种类型的吸猫人？", "description": "你把猫当做宠物、朋友、孩子、主人、社交道具，还是只是叶公好猫？（题图来自：SketchPort）", "record_count": 6903, "comment_count": 54, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20170710102501wkuY05UsTJKCfIFg.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 1, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2017-07-10T17:00:00Z", "questions": [{"id": 2583, "title": "你是哪种类型的吸猫人？", "content": "你是哪种类型的吸猫人？", "genre": 2, "options": [{"id": 220220, "content": "云养猫，关注了不少萌宠博主，吸猫片成为日常", "image": "img/option/option/20170710102620TpkcsPDJrxXtU60R.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 220221, "content": "铲屎官，家有猫星人，猫是我很好的朋友/亲人/主人", "image": "img/option/option/20170710102652EY5SQRva7oP3C6iw.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 220222, "content": "猫下属，公司有猫，是我应聘的一个很大理由", "image": "img/option/option/20170710102758y3rxRZaqHwbO4V9e.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 220223, "content": "路人关照型，在路上碰到萌猫总想撸一撸", "image": "img/option/option/20170710102840NSYTstvhpCwbyqex.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 220225, "content": "猫友，自己不养猫，但会去朋友家or猫咖啡馆撸猫", "image": "img/option/option/20170710102939KdC3qjn471FzhXsw.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 220224, "content": "被动接受型，身边的朋友喜欢猫而接触，猫片/表情包更多作为社交道具", "image": "img/option/option/20170710102911gGPxZL86rV5iXIyQ.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 220226, "content": "叶公好猫型，关于猫的周边和影视舞剧会买或看，真猫则保持距离", "image": "img/option/option/20170710103049RfehwHP5EjFctk2o.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 220227, "content": "冷感型，对猫无动于衷", "image": "img/option/option/20170710103040o1tGbsYrIJaKjxyM.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}]}]}